| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-4587 — Recovery Inhibition (nokoyawa)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: bbef7624-8ee4-5295-ac19-cfd6dcd13a0c"
